<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ shì pú táo shù 迦南887</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ shì pú táo shù, wǒ men shì zhī zi. zhī zi lián yú pú táo shù.
 wǒ men cháng zài zhǔ lǐ miàn, zhǔ yě cháng zài wǒ men lǐ miàn. zhǔ bì shí shí kàn gù,
 zài xǐ lè zhōng xǐ lè, zài méng fú zhōng méng fú. bù pà fēng chuī yǔ lín yán hán kù shǔ,
 zhǔ shì pú táo shù, wǒ men shì zhī zi. zhī zi lián yú pú táo shù.
 zhī zi lián yú pú táo shù.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>887</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>